    "rich_text_R6yrtQ": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "subheading_Cb4Y3W": {
          "type": "subheading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Choosing Tyroler BrightTools over other magnetic window cleaners offers a variety of benefits, such as:"
          }
        },
        "heading_iPYKg6": {
          "type": "heading",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "text": "",
            "heading_tag": "h1",
            "text_color": "",
            "gradient": ""
          }
        },
        "richtext_xzBQUP": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p></p><ul><li>Quality materials: Tyroler BrightTools uses rare earth magnets, metal, ABS, and 100% natural rubber to construct their magnetic window cleaners. This ensures that the product is durable and long-lasting.</li><li>Safe to use: Tyroler BrightTools uses fine microfiber cloths that are detergent-resistant and can be reused up to 300 times. This reduces the chance of scratches on the glass surface and ensures that the product is safe to use.</li><li>Cost-effective: The company offers replacement cloths, so you don’t have to purchase the whole product again when the cloths need to be replaced. This can save you money in the long run.</li><li>Eco-friendly: Tyroler BrightTools uses eco-friendly materials in their products and encourages reusability, which helps to save the environment.</li><li>Durable and long-lasting: The company ensures that the product is built to last a long time, reducing the need for frequent replacements, and saving you money in the long run.</li></ul><p>In summary, choosing Tyroler BrightTools over other magnetic window cleaners offers quality, safety, cost-effectiveness, eco-friendliness and durability.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
